                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/6765.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mexico City</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-02-11T14:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 11, 1913—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have been notified informally by Díaz that if he is successful in the battle
                    today, he will expect that the United States will immediately recognize his
                    belligerency.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
